    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the standard of automotive excellence with this pristine, showroom-quality vehicle. Meticulously preserved and showing in absolute peak condition, this car offers a driving experience that is indistinguishable from its first day on the road. From the flawless finish to the untouched interior, every aspect of this vehicle has been curated for the most demanding owner. This is a rare opportunity to secure a premier specimen that defines quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
